Decentrathon 4.0 is the largest AI hackathon in Kazakhstan. This September, Decentrathon returns in an offline format, spanning 20 regions across the country. The event will bring together developers and AI enthusiasts to create innovative solutions, exchange knowledge, and foster the growth of the AI ecosystem in Kazakhstan.
